<h2>Methodology</h2>

<h4><strong>LOWER MINIMUM QUANTITATIVE LEVELS - WHY?</strong></h4>
<p>Via memo's published by EPA Executives, Offices have been directed to integrate the use of lower MQL's for NPDES permitting. To reach the new mercury MQL, speical sampling and laboratory techniques are needed.<p>

