            <strong>The Hanlon Memo</strong>
        </p>

        <p style="margin-left: 100px; margin-right: 100px">“… in the light of existing regulatory requirements for NPDES permitting, only the most sensitive methods such as Methods 1631E and 245.7 are appropriate in most instances for use in deciding whether
