        <p style="margin-left: 100px; margin-right: 100px">EPA Region 6 has “… revised the MQL’s (Minimum Quantification Levels) which we will be accepting for EPA issued permits. … Region 6 expects that you (delegated States) will revise your procedures to
            incorporate these revised MQL’s” into your permitting procedures.</p>
        <p style="margin-left: 100px; margin-right: 100px">Claudia V. Hosch, Chief<br>
